column5: Anyone from here fishing in the walleye turny on the grand river tomorow??....i'll be the one winning it but might be worth the excitment anyway,,,lol

WOW...I didnt know that there was a walleye tourney anywhere in ontario this weekend!!!! its pretty late in the year for a sanctioned tournament for walleye but hey what the heck right???   can you give anymore details,location,times and maybe there will be some members wanting to go and give it a try.....thanks for posting   cheers
Down Shawn Down!!!  I know you're trying to figure out a way to get there....but dont do it....LOL
Boats loaded with tackle and rods and on the truck already to go 4;00am Im outa here see you there.
Me Me... Don't forget ME in the morning Sonny... and that would be WE if anyone wins... hehehe  You always forget my expertise and advice helps you win these things...
